      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.qIIoypmTFypnmRer]{Evolutionist Adaption}</p>\n<p>In a pinch, you can rapidly shed the outermost layers of your skin. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to all saves against the burning and entangled conditions, and a +2 circumstance bonus to your KAC against grapple combat maneuvers. If you would fail a saving throw and gain the burning or entangled condition, you can spend 3 MP and reroll that saving throw as a reaction. If you would become grappled by a creature, you can spend 3 MP as a reaction to force that creature to reroll their attack roll to resolve the grapple.</p>"
